        Constructor.
        参数:
        bucketName - Bucket name.
        prefix - Prefix filter---returned Live Channels must start with this prefix.
        marker - Marker filter----returned Live Channels must be greater than this marker in lexicographical order.
        maxKeys - Max Live Channels to return, By default it's 100.
